            "exec": [
              "var response = pm.response.json();",
              "if (response.results && response.results.length > 0) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"listingId\", response.results[0]._id);",
              "    console.log(\"First listing ID saved: \" + response.results[0]._id);",
              "    console.log(\"Total listings found: \" + response.results.length);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "packages": {},
            "requests": {}
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/listings",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "listings"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "city",
              "value": "Fort Lauderdale",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "state",
              "value": "Florida",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "country",
              "value": "United States of America",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "checkIn",
              "value": "2026-04-15",
              "description": "YYYY-MM-DD format",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "checkOut",
              "value": "2026-04-20",
              "description": "YYYY-MM-DD format",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "guests",
              "value": "4",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "numberOfBedrooms",
              "value": "3",
              "description": "Returns 3+ bedrooms (minimum, not exact)",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "limit",
              "value": "1",
              "description": "number of listings api returns",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "fields",
              "value": "_id title address pictures prices bedrooms bathrooms accommodates amenities",
              "description": "if selected api will return only those fields that are mentioned and ignore the ones which are not mentioned in the fields value",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "cursor",
              "value": "eyJuZXh0Q3Vyc29yIjp7Imxpc3RpbmdJZCI6IjY5MTYzZGJhYjhmNDI2MDAxMzJhNDZhNiJ9fQ==",
              "description": "add the cursro value from the response to get the next pagingated listings ",
              "type": "text",
              "disabled": true
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## How Pagination Works\n\nThe API uses **cursor-based pagination** (not page numbers). Notice in your response:\n\n``` json\n\"pagination\": {\n    \"total\": 69,\n    \"cursor\": {\n        \"next\": \"eyJuZXh0Q3Vyc29yIj...\"   ŌåÉ this is your \"next page\" key\n    }\n}\n\n ```\n\n> You have **69 total listings** available. \n  \n\nTo get the next 20 listings, add the cursor value as a query parameter:\n\n```\nGET /api/listings?cursor=eyJuZXh0Q3Vyc29yIj...\n\n ```\n\nKeep using the `next` cursor from each response until `cursor.next` comes back as `null` ŌĆö that means you've reached the last page.\n\nTo get **all 69 listings at once**, set `limit=100` (that's the maximum allowed).\n\n---\n\n## Query Parameters Reference\n\n### Pagination\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `limit` | `20` | Max 100, default 20 |\n| `cursor` | _(from previous response)_ | For next page |\n\n---\n\n### Dates & Guests\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `checkIn` | `2025-08-01` | Format: YYYY-MM-DD |\n| `checkOut` | `2025-08-05` | Format: YYYY-MM-DD |\n| `guests` | `4` | Total number of guests |\n\n---\n\n### Location\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `city` | `Fort Lauderdale` | Must include `country` too |\n| `country` | `United States` | Required when using `city` |\n| `state` | `Florida` | Optional |\n| `neighborhood` | `Downtown` | Optional |\n| `minLat` / `maxLat` | `26.1` / `26.3` | Geo bounding box |\n| `minLng` / `maxLng` | `-80.2` / `-80.0` | Geo bounding box |\n\n---\n\n### Property Filters\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `numberOfBedrooms` | `2` | Minimum value (2+) |\n| `numberOfBathrooms` | `1` | Minimum value |\n| `minOccupancy` | `4` | Minimum guest capacity |\n| `propertyType` | `HOUSE` | `APARTMENT`, `VILLA`, `CABIN`, etc. |\n| `listingType` | `SINGLE` | `SINGLE` or `MTL` |\n| `roomType` | `ENTIRE_HOME_APT` | `PRIVATE_ROOM`, `SHARED_ROOM` |\n\n---\n\n### Price Range\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `minPrice` | `100` | Must include `currency` |\n| `maxPrice` | `500` | Must include `currency` |\n| `currency` | `USD` | Required with price filters |\n\n---\n\n### Amenities\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `includeAmenities` | `POOL,WIFI,PETS_ALLOWED` | Comma-separated |\n| `excludeAmenities` | `SMOKING_ALLOWED` | Comma-separated |\n| `petsAllowed` | `true` | Boolean |\n| `smokingAllowed` | `false` | Boolean |\n\n---\n\n### Bed Types\n\n| Parameter | Example | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `kingBed` | `1` | Minimum number required |\n| `queenBed` | `2` | Minimum number required |\n\n---\n\n### Fields (Request Only What You Need)\n\nUse the `fields` parameter to limit the response to specific properties and reduce payload size:\n\n```\nfields=_id title address pictures prices bedrooms bathrooms accommodates amenities reviews\n\n ```"
      },
      "response": []
    },
